Definition: abnormal condition in which vision for distant objects is better than for near objects
Synonyms: adj, all, farsighted, hyperopic, myopia, hypermetropia, hypermetropic, hypermetropy, farsightedness, longsightedness, longsighted, ametropia, abnormal, condition, in, which, vision, for, distant, objects, is, better, than, near
Category: noun.state
